overview.en: ZBG is a wholly-owned subsidiary platform of ZB.COM, one of the world's top five exchanges. ZBG is positioned as a light and fast global trading platform. ZT is the platform currency of the ZBG trading platform.
overview.zh: ZBG是全球前五的交易所ZB.COM全资控股子平台，ZBG全新定位于轻盈快捷的全球化交易平台，不仅在技术上是ZB的集大成者，在经营理念上也有众多创新。ZT是ZBG交易平台的平台币。
